high_descs: turn around to face the microwave
open the cabinet above microwave, take out salt shaker, close the door
turn to the left to face the sink
put the salt shaker on the counter on the right side
open the cabinet above the sink on the right
take out the salt shaker from the cabinet, close the door
turn completely around in the same spot in the kitchen
put the salt shaker to the left of the other salt shaker on the counter to the right
anns.task_desc: put two salt shakers on the counter

high_descs: Turn right, walk toward the sink, then turn right to go to the microwave.
Take the pepper mill from the cabinet above the microwave.
Turn left to face the sink.
Put the pepper mill on the counter, above the dishwasher.
Look up to the cabinet above the counter.
Open the cabinet and take the pepper mill from inside.
Look back down at the sink.
Place the pepper mill on the counter, next to the other pepper mill.
anns.task_desc: Put two pepper mills on the counter.

high_descs: Go to the cupboard above the microwave
Take a saltshaker out
Turn to the sink
Put the saltshaker on the counter
Look at the cupboard above the sink
Take saltshaker out of the cupboard above the sink
Turn around and look at the sink
Put the saltshaker on the counter
anns.task_desc: Move two saltshakers out of cupboards onto the countertop
